text:
Generative Artificial Intelligence
is creating a future where AI

will impact humans in ways
we can only imagine today.

Hi, I'm James Landay,
I'm here to welcome you

to our program on Generative
AI and Foundation Models.
In this program,
we'll explore Generative AI
from a diverse set of
expert perspectives.
We've invited the most
renowned faculty and instructors
at Stanford University
to give you a truly unique
learning experience.

They'll share their cutting edge
research and insights,
allowing you to delve deep

into the ever evolving
 landscape of Generative AI.

We've divided our journey
into three individual courses.

You'll be exploring topics
like technical fundamentals,
how foundation models
can be applied in different business fields,

and emphasis on 
human-centered design.

Together, we'll navigate
the evolving landscape of Generative AI,
demonstrating how and where
human values will lead the way.
